1
00:01:30,211 --> 00:01:32,531
[Episode 2]

2
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,100
I am Princess Rong Le of Western Qi.

3
00:01:43,100 --> 00:01:46,600
It's my honor to meet Your Majesty.

4
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:48,200
At ease, Princess.

5
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,600
Rise.

6
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:51,600
Much obliged, Your Majesty.

7
00:01:55,244 --> 00:01:56,796
- Xiao Sha.
- Yes, Princess.

8
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:59,200
Present the gift to His Majesty.

9
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,400
Yes, Princess.

10
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,200
Bring it in.

11
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:06,100
Your Majesty, in order to thank you for your generous gift,

12
00:02:06,100 --> 00:02:08,000
my brother has prepared this returning gift.

13
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:10,200
Please accept it.

14
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:21,400
White jade glaze cup.

15
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:25,100
Word is, this white jade glaze cup has been here for hundreds of years.

16
00:02:25,100 --> 00:02:29,200
There is only a pair of these in this world and they are priceless.

17
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:32,800
If you use them to drink tea, the tea will be fragrant and refreshing.

18
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:35,200
If you use them to drink water in summer,

19
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:38,600
they can cool you off, quench your thirst and you'll feel invigorated.

20
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,000
And your body will be revived.

21
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,400
These cups are really intriguing.

22
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:46,100
The Emperor of Qi has given me such a treasure.

23
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:49,400
Minister Yang, write a letter for me.

24
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:52,500
I want to express my thanks to the Emperor of Western Qi.

25
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:56,000
Your Majesty,

26
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,900
before our princess departed to come here,

27
00:02:57,900 --> 00:03:02,500
my emperor had ordered me to pass on his words to you.

28
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:04,900
What is it that the Emperor of Qi has to say?

29
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:06,300
He said that...

30
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:09,400
the white jade glaze cups are indeed rare treasures.

31
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:13,000
But they are incomparable to Princess Rong Le...

32
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,100
who took a high place in his heart.

33
00:03:15,100 --> 00:03:17,800
He hopes that your country can treat our princess well.

34
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:21,300
By doing so, the hundred-year deal between us two will be secured.

35
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:23,000
Of course.

36
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:26,000
Princess Rong Le is the peace ambassador between our two countries.

37
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,400
She is undoubtedly an honored guest of our country.

38
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,800
And she will be marrying my son.

39
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:33,400
We will give her the best treatment.

40
00:03:34,700 --> 00:03:38,600
Your Majesty, Prince Li...

41
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,100
What is wrong with him?

42
00:03:40,100 --> 00:03:42,700
I have already summoned him for more than two hours.

43
00:03:42,700 --> 00:03:44,000
Where is he?

44
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:48,200
Servants in Prince Li's Manor said that Prince Li is resting.

45
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:50,400
So, he cannot attend the court.

46
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:55,900
- Wuyu.
- Yes, Father.

47
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:57,600
Go to Prince Li's Manor to summon him.

48
00:03:57,600 --> 00:04:01,200
Bring him to the court no matter what you have to do.

49
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:03,300
Yes, Father.

50
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:23,900
Wuyou, come out!

51
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,200
Wuyou, I beg you.

52
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:29,000
Let's attend the court, all right?

53
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:31,400
[Simple and Unadorned]

54
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:39,400
Wuyou.

55
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:42,800
If you don't come out, I'll be sent to the royal tomb.

56
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,800
Your Highness.

57
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,600
We can't continue like this.

58
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:49,400
His Majesty is still waiting for us.

59
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:58,000
Don't blame me then.

60
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:05,200
Father, Wuyou is here.

61
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:08,500
Prince Li has arrived.

62
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:08,200
Insolent! How dare he come here in this manner?

63
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,700
Father.

64
00:06:09,700 --> 00:06:12,400
Just now, you told me to use any way I can...

65
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:14,300
to bring Wuyou to the court. Right?

66
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:16,200
Shut up!

67
00:06:34,700 --> 00:06:37,400
Scoundrel, get up now!

68
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:42,900
Wuyou, don't be rude.

69
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:46,000
The princess is the peace ambassador between our two countries.

70
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:49,100
I already prepared your wedding suit for you. Change into it quickly.

71
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:51,200
We'll seal this engagement in the great hall today,

72
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:53,600
and you'll get married as soon as possible.

73
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:13,700
When did I agree to getting married?

74
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:30,200
Your marriage is already set.

75
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:33,500
Whether you agree or not, this marriage will go on.

76
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:35,000
Guards!

77
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,800
- Change the clothes for Prince Li.
- Yes, Your Majesty!

78
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:47,900
Your Majesty,

79
00:07:49,100 --> 00:07:51,600
do you really want to use force?

80
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,800
If you really don't want to do it,

81
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:57,200
I can find another person to get married in your stead.

82
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:59,000
Wuyu.

83
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:01,800
Father.

84
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:06,000
Since you can find a stand-in for my marriage,

85
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:09,800
how about letting him consummate the marriage, too?

86
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,400
Scoundrel, how dare you say that.

87
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:14,600
I won't marry her.

88
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:18,300
If you really want to forge an alliance with Western Qi through marriage,

89
00:08:18,300 --> 00:08:20,700
please choose another person.

90
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,600
I'm not sure about other things...

91
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,200
but in this Northern Lin,

92
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:29,000
we have a lot of princes.

93
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,100
You were chosen by the Emperor of Qi.

94
00:08:31,100 --> 00:08:32,600
The marriage is already set.

95
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,800
How can you just change it?

96
00:08:39,700 --> 00:08:41,300
Your Majesty.

97
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:44,800
Please allow me to speak my mind.

98
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:50,000
Please do, Princess.

99
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:52,800
When I was coming to Northern Lin, I was thinking...

100
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:56,500
about what my future husband would be like.

101
00:08:56,500 --> 00:09:00,400
I was thinking that even though he might not be perfect,

102
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:03,200
at least he would not behave like this.

103
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,800
The Northern Lin's marriage proposal...

104
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:07,500
had described Prince Li highly.

105
00:09:07,500 --> 00:09:10,200
It said that he was courteous,

106
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:13,400
brave, intelligent, and extremely resourceful.

107
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:17,600
But the Prince Li that I see is not courteous.

108
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,400
He is arrogant and rude.

109
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:22,000
He is not brave and intelligent. Just fallacious reasoning.

110
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:25,400
He is not resourceful. Instead, he is wilful and wild.

111
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:27,600
Just like a kid that will never grow up.

112
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:30,000
He acts like a spoiled child in public.

113
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:38,800
I understand.

114
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:42,000
Mutual consent is needed in a marriage.

115
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:44,500
I too, want to marry a husband of my choice.

116
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:46,700
And I want to have a happy and beautiful life.

117
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:50,000
I don't want to move so far away from my country to get married.

118
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,800
But for the benefit of my country,

119
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:54,600
I came to this country out of duty.

120
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:57,300
I as a woman can do that...

121
00:09:57,300 --> 00:10:01,200
while a manly prince like you keeps on rejecting it.

122
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:05,600
Can't you take this righteous cause for your country?

123
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:22,000
So all in all, you are set on me.

124
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:24,600
That might not be true.

125
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:36,400
I just hope that you can give us a chance to know each other.

126
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:40,900
But if you still haven't change your mind after half a year,

127
00:10:40,900 --> 00:10:42,800
I'll do as you say.

128
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:46,000
I'll marry another without complaint.

129
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:48,400
You sounded so righteous.

130
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:50,300
But in my opinion,

131
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:53,400
a strong country does not rely on alliance through marriage.

132
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:57,200
Only the weak will cower behind the skirts of a lady...

133
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:59,700
to hide his own weaknesses.

134
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:00,900
Of course,

135
00:11:00,900 --> 00:11:05,400
your self-sacrificing spirit today is very touching.

136
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:07,000
But I, Zongzheng Wuyou,

137
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:11,300
will not exchange my marriage for some benefits.

138
00:11:11,300 --> 00:11:15,500
I'm not interested at all... in your half-a-year deal.

139
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:20,900
Do you have no interest or do you have no confidence?

140
00:11:21,900 --> 00:11:23,800
You gave excuses and wanted to escape.

141
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:26,300
Are you afraid that you'll lose to me?

142
00:11:30,300 --> 00:11:32,400
A taunt.

143
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:34,200
You said that you were strong.

144
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:37,000
Are you afraid to take on this bet?

145
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:42,000
Looks like the famous Prince Li...

146
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:44,400
is not that impressive after all.

147
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:50,800
We'll do as the princess has said. Half a year it is.

148
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:52,300
This court is adjourned.

149
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:12,000
Wuyou, I think your plan will fail this time.

150
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:14,500
Princess Rong Le is not an easy opponent.

151
00:12:14,500 --> 00:12:17,300
What if she still forces you to marry her after half a year?

152
00:12:17,300 --> 00:12:20,400
Nobody can force me against my will.

153
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:23,600
Although it's rumored that she is ugly, she has a nice voice.

154
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,800
She has a sharp tongue, too.

155
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:27,100
It'll be fun to bicker with her.

156
00:12:27,100 --> 00:12:29,400
Wuyou, how about just marrying her?

157
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:31,200
If you admire her so much,

158
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:33,000
you can marry her.

159
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:36,200
No. She is too capable.

160
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:38,000
I can't handle her.

161
00:12:39,337 --> 00:12:40,900
Greetings, Your Highness.

162
00:12:40,900 --> 00:12:42,800
His Majesty has summoned Prince Li.

163
00:12:42,800 --> 00:12:44,600
I don't have time for him.

164
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:48,300
If you don't have time to come to me, how about I come to you?

165
00:12:55,223 --> 00:12:56,469
Father.

166
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:03,200
Father, I'll take my leave first.

167
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,500
Let's go.

168
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:10,900
I know.

169
00:13:12,100 --> 00:13:16,100
You still bear a grudge towards me for the things that happened in the past.

170
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:18,800
All these years, you paid no attention to the country's affairs...

171
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:20,400
and you didn't attend court.

172
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:22,300
You don't even want to see me.

173
00:13:22,300 --> 00:13:24,200
And I let you.

174
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:28,300
But today's matter holds great importance for our country.

175
00:13:28,300 --> 00:13:31,400
You can't act recklessly about it.

176
00:13:36,300 --> 00:13:38,800
During the war against Wei last time,

177
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:40,900
the crown prince had directed the armies with ill-ease.

178
00:13:40,900 --> 00:13:43,600
In the end, they lost and fled from the war until they were...

179
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:46,800
forced by the Wei Army to strip off their armor. Such disgrace.

180
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:49,400
I have to bring back the honor of our country.

181
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:52,000
So, I have to declare war against Wei again.

182
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:55,500
And having an alliance with Western Qi can strengthen our hold.

183
00:13:55,500 --> 00:13:57,600
It is of vital importance for our country.

184
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:59,800
Crown Prince is the one who made the mistake in the war with Wei.

185
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:01,500
What has it got to do with me?

186
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:04,200
I already made an exception by helping out with the issue in the south.

187
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:06,300
What else do you want?

188
00:14:07,300 --> 00:14:09,700
I was very glad when you lent a helping hand...

189
00:14:09,700 --> 00:14:11,400
with the issue in the south.

190
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:12,900
It shows that in your heart,

191
00:14:12,900 --> 00:14:16,000
you still care for the country.

192
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:20,800
Wuyou, if you can forget the past...

193
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:23,400
and let go of the prejudice and resentment towards me,

194
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:27,600
with your brilliance, you'll pioneer a great undertaking in the future.

195
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:29,500
You want me to forget the past?

196
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:31,200
Impossible.

197
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:33,400
And it's impossible that I'll marry...

198
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:35,200
that princess from Western Qi after half a year.

199
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:37,400
Your Majesty.

200
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:42,200
You are the one bent on using women to consolidate your power.

201
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:44,200
As for what I want,

202
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:47,600
I'll get it honorably with my own capability.

203
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:50,000
Wuyou.

204
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:54,500
Recently, my body is not as strong as before.

205
00:14:54,500 --> 00:14:56,400
I'm already past my prime.

206
00:14:56,400 --> 00:15:02,000
This country... needs a capable and reliable heir.

207
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,800
You are still in the prime of manhood.

208
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:06,400
You have so many women and sons.

209
00:15:06,400 --> 00:15:09,200
Your heir is the crown prince.

210
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:11,600
It has nothing to do with me.

211
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:22,200
This princess is as spoiled and wilful as the rumors said.

212
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:26,400
I never thought that this arrogant Prince Li would suffer too.

213
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:32,300
He always looked down on me because His Majesty dotes on him.

214
00:15:32,300 --> 00:15:34,200
This princess...

215
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:38,400
has helped me to vent out my grievance towards him.

216
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:42,500
I think that this arranged marriage between Prince Li and the princess...

217
00:15:42,500 --> 00:15:45,800
will be very unfavorable to you.

218
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:48,100
If Prince Li really marries the princess of Western Qi,

219
00:15:48,100 --> 00:15:50,500
his might will be redoubled.

220
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:53,900
And sooner or later, he will threaten your position.

221
00:15:54,900 --> 00:15:57,400
Minister Yu, you worry too much.

222
00:15:57,400 --> 00:16:00,100
Before my father regained his lands back then,

223
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:04,600
as the eldest, I had gone into war by his side far and wide.

224
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:07,000
I'm so much more popular than Wuyou...

225
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,600
who paid no attention to the country's affairs.

226
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:11,600
Even though I lost in the war with Wei,

227
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:15,200
my father has never tried to demote me.

228
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:17,400
As for this Prince Li,

229
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:19,600
do you think they will really get married...

230
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:21,900
based on today's situation?

231
00:16:21,900 --> 00:16:23,600
How wise of you.

232
00:16:23,600 --> 00:16:25,800
You outmatch your opponent.

233
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:43,600
Your Majesty, Princess Rong Le has reached Northern Lin safely.

234
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:47,000
And she has entered the palace to meet the emperor of Northern Lin.

235
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:24,200
Have you released the kite to search for a highly skilled doctor as I had ordered?
(Kite is the common name for certain birds of prey)

236
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:27,500
We had sent a team to Winter Mountain and other places the doctor went, to search for him.

237
00:17:27,500 --> 00:17:30,200
Her Majesty has arrived!

238
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:33,600
- Step out first.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

239
00:17:52,700 --> 00:17:55,300
Greetings, Mother.

240
00:17:56,100 --> 00:17:58,800
- Rise.
- Thank you, Mother.

241
00:18:02,900 --> 00:18:06,200
I had reminded you time after time.

242
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:08,300
Those who seek to be successful...

243
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:12,100
have to be ruthless and incisive.

244
00:18:12,100 --> 00:18:14,900
Rather to bear brief, sharp pains than lasting ones.

245
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:17,000
Thank you for your teachings.

246
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:20,600
Have you investigated the assassination done to you by Chen...

247
00:18:20,600 --> 00:18:22,800
when you went out from the palace?

248
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:25,000
Don't you know that...

249
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:28,200
those people had already been silenced by death?

250
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:50,400
Greetings, My Princess.

251
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,500
We have reached the Princess Manor.

252
00:18:51,500 --> 00:18:54,000
Please get off of the carriage.

253
00:18:59,661 --> 00:19:02,216
[Princess Manor]

254
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:11,200
His Majesty had decreed.

255
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:13,800
Princess Rong Le is an honored guest of Northern Lin.

256
00:19:13,800 --> 00:19:16,400
Make sure to serve her well. Give her the best treatment.

257
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:18,800
We'll do as his command.

258
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:20,500
This way please, Princess.

259
00:19:22,800 --> 00:19:24,400
You are our honored guest.

260
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:26,800
We should be the one responsible for your safety.

261
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:29,100
Your entourage is new here.

262
00:19:29,100 --> 00:19:30,600
They are not familiar with this place.

263
00:19:30,600 --> 00:19:33,500
They need to get used to it slowly.

264
00:19:33,500 --> 00:19:35,400
Your guard will be staying temporarily in a post-house.

265
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:37,500
No need to worry about them.

266
00:19:38,300 --> 00:19:39,900
I don't mind with the others.

267
00:19:39,900 --> 00:19:43,000
But my personal bodyguard, Xiao Sha, was sent by my brother.

268
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:45,300
Before I left, my brother especially reminded me that...

269
00:19:45,300 --> 00:19:47,600
I can't let this guard leave my side.

270
00:19:47,600 --> 00:19:49,600
If he even has to stay in a post-house,

271
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:52,600
I would not know how to explain to my brother.

272
00:19:53,600 --> 00:19:55,400
All right.

273
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:57,000
Let him through.

274
00:19:57,800 --> 00:19:59,300
This way please, Princess.

275
00:20:03,600 --> 00:20:06,200
This manor was specially made for you, Princess.

276
00:20:06,200 --> 00:20:09,400
The design in this place was made according to your likings.

277
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:12,200
We hope that you'll find this a home away from home.

278
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:17,200
His Majesty is deeply apologetic for the things that happened yesterday.

279
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:20,200
He has specially prepared some gifts as a way of expressing that.

280
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:22,200
Thank His Majesty for his kindness.

281
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:24,200
Madam Qiu Yi.

282
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:28,400
She is the housekeeper of this manor, Qiu Yi.

283
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:30,900
You can go to her if you need anything.

284
00:20:30,900 --> 00:20:32,800
Greetings, Princess.

285
00:20:32,800 --> 00:20:34,200
Be at ease.

286
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:37,400
I won't keep you from resting then, Princess.

287
00:20:40,700 --> 00:20:42,600
You may leave too.

288
00:20:44,590 --> 00:20:45,700
Anything else?

289
00:20:45,700 --> 00:20:48,000
You are still an unmarried lady.

290
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:50,600
Although Captain Xiao is with you,

291
00:20:50,600 --> 00:20:52,200
he is still a man.

292
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:55,200
According to the rules, he can only stay in the outer courtyard.

293
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:56,800
I am the Princess of Western Qi.

294
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:59,800
As long as I'm still unmarried, I'll still be a Western Qi citizen.

295
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:02,400
This is none of your concern. You may leave.

296
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:04,000
Live in the same way as locals do.

297
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:07,000
Please don't make it difficult for me.

298
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:09,700
I'm entrusted by His Majesty to take care of Princess Manor.

299
00:21:09,700 --> 00:21:11,000
I'm just following the rules.

300
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:13,400
What are the rules?

301
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:16,200
Since His Majesty has given me a manor with Western Qi design,

302
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:19,400
here, my words are the rules.

303
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:21,100
Leave.

304
00:21:23,800 --> 00:21:26,600
Looks like you are not willing to obey my order as well.

305
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:30,800
If that's the case, I won't be staying in this Princess Manor.

306
00:21:30,800 --> 00:21:32,300
Let's go.

307
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:36,496
Princess.

308
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:39,600
Princess.

309
00:21:39,600 --> 00:21:42,400
Please calm down, Princess. I don't mean to disobey you.

310
00:21:42,400 --> 00:21:44,400
I'm just doing it for your own good.

311
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:46,000
Xiao Sha.

312
00:21:48,500 --> 00:21:50,800
Captain Xiao, what are you doing?

313
00:21:50,800 --> 00:21:53,200
I should be the one asking you.

314
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:54,900
How dare you block the princess's path.

315
00:21:54,900 --> 00:21:56,400
What are you trying to do?

316
00:21:56,400 --> 00:21:58,200
I want to ask His Majesty.

317
00:21:58,200 --> 00:22:00,200
Are you treating me as an honored guest...

318
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:02,000
or are you trying to cage me?

319
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:03,700
You have overstated things.

320
00:22:03,700 --> 00:22:07,200
I can do nothing when Prince Li rejected the marriage.

321
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:10,200
But if the servants in my manor dare to disobey me...

322
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:12,500
I think Prince Li wouldn't blame her...

323
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:15,400
for killing one or two of her servants to vent out her anger.

324
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:17,800
Please spare my life. I've learned my mistake.

325
00:22:17,800 --> 00:22:19,500
You are the mistress in this manor.

326
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:22,000
If you insist that Captain Xiao should stay here,

327
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:23,700
I won't dare to stop you.

328
00:22:23,700 --> 00:22:25,400
But if you want to leave the manor,

329
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:26,800
even if you kill me,

330
00:22:26,800 --> 00:22:29,000
I'll have to send some guards from the manor to go with you...

331
00:22:29,000 --> 00:22:30,700
in order to protect you.

332
00:22:30,700 --> 00:22:33,900
If something dangerous happens to you, even my death...

333
00:22:33,900 --> 00:22:35,900
wouldn't be enough for me to atone for my sins.

334
00:23:02,600 --> 00:23:05,000
Prince Li of Northern Lin, Zongzheng Wuyou,

335
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:07,200
is a very talented man,

336
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:10,300
the sole disciple of Qin Yong, ex-chief Minister of Northern Lin.

337
00:23:10,300 --> 00:23:13,000
So, it's very possible that he has...

338
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:16,800
"The Book of Mountains and Rivers" written by Qin Yong.

339
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:19,600
- The Book of Mountains and Rivers?
- That's right.

340
00:23:19,600 --> 00:23:21,600
The Book of Mountains and Rivers...

341
00:23:21,600 --> 00:23:23,700
has recorded the rise and dip of the mountains,

342
00:23:23,700 --> 00:23:26,400
the cities, the pools, and strategic places from all over the world.

343
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:29,400
It has detailed information about astronomy, geography, meteorology...

344
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:32,500
and the fastest way to win a war.

345
00:23:32,500 --> 00:23:36,500
So, there is a rumor that...

346
00:23:36,500 --> 00:23:40,000
those who possess the book will possess the world.

347
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:42,200
If I can get my hands on this book within half a year,

348
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:45,400
I can go back to Western Qi and stay by my brother's side.

349
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:47,200
- Princess.
- Do you have the information?

350
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:49,000
Yes. It's in Moon Embrace Teahouse.

351
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:51,000
All right. I have to go out for a while.

352
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:53,400
You want to go out alone?

353
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:55,800
This Princess Manor is heavily guarded.

354
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:58,800
We need to find a way if I want to go out.

355
00:23:58,800 --> 00:24:00,600
All right, Princess.

356
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:04,200
Madam!

357
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:07,000
Madam, such beautiful flowers.

358
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:09,200
You just plucked them for the princess, right?

359
00:24:09,200 --> 00:24:11,300
How kind of you, Madam.

360
00:24:11,300 --> 00:24:14,800
Miss Ling Yue, the princess is our mistress.

361
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:16,800
It's only right to serve her.

362
00:24:16,800 --> 00:24:18,800
But you are not our mistress.

363
00:24:18,800 --> 00:24:21,800
This pot of flowers is very expensive.

364
00:24:21,800 --> 00:24:24,600
What if you break it?

365
00:24:26,000 --> 00:24:29,600
Madam, let me bring it in for you.

366
00:24:29,600 --> 00:24:32,600
Have you no regard for the rules?

367
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:34,600
Ever since the princess moved here,

368
00:24:34,600 --> 00:24:38,500
as the housekeeper, I don't even have the chance to meet her.

369
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:41,000
It's all because of you and Lian Xin.

370
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:43,200
Princess gave the order to not let you in.

371
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:47,400
How dare you threaten me with the princess.

372
00:24:52,100 --> 00:24:54,400
Captain Xiao.

373
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:55,800
This is just a misunderstanding.

374
00:24:55,800 --> 00:24:58,800
It's just that I haven't been serving the princess lately.

375
00:24:58,800 --> 00:25:00,600
Those who know...

376
00:25:00,600 --> 00:25:02,900
will know that those two have served the princess well.

377
00:25:02,900 --> 00:25:05,700
Those who don't will think that the princess is being petty...

378
00:25:05,700 --> 00:25:09,400
and is still mad at me for the incident last time.

379
00:25:10,800 --> 00:25:13,500
Madam, you think too much.

380
00:25:13,500 --> 00:25:15,000
Our princess is very magnanimous.

381
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:17,400
She just complimented you just now.

382
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:19,000
She said that you are very meticulous.

383
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:22,200
And you ensured that everything in the manor runs smoothly.

384
00:25:22,200 --> 00:25:26,000
By the way, the princess is going to award you.

385
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:29,300
She had asked you to gather everybody in the garden.

386
00:25:29,300 --> 00:25:32,000
She wants to award everybody at once.

387
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:36,000
I'll leave this to you then, Miss Lian Xin.

388
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:47,900
Thank you, Captain Xiao.

389
00:26:04,120 --> 00:26:08,080
[Blessed With Latent Auspiciousness]

390
00:26:10,050 --> 00:26:12,799
Please give these out to everybody.

391
00:26:12,800 --> 00:26:16,300
Please ask the kitchen to prepare more food for tonight.

392
00:26:16,300 --> 00:26:18,800
Tonight, there will be a feast for everybody.

393
00:26:18,800 --> 00:26:22,300
- Thank you, Princess.
- Thank you, Princess.

394
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:26,000
There are enough for everybody.

395
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:27,800
Don't fight for them.

396
00:26:34,988 --> 00:26:36,606
Take it. This is for you.

397
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:50,300
Wuyou, no need to strike out at father every time you see him.

398
00:26:50,300 --> 00:26:53,000
Actually, he cares for you the most.

399
00:26:54,600 --> 00:26:57,800
All right. I won't talk about it anymore.

400
00:26:57,800 --> 00:27:00,300
Wuyou, look.

401
00:27:00,300 --> 00:27:02,400
Look at what I've brought you.

402
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:05,800
Take a look.

403
00:27:11,400 --> 00:27:14,800
- This is a good tea.
- Of course it is.

404
00:27:14,800 --> 00:27:16,800
This tea set is not a normal tea set as well.

405
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:19,800
I got this treasure from the Rare Item Chest in Moon Embrace Teahouse.

406
00:27:19,800 --> 00:27:21,800
I heard that this Rare Item Chest contains...

407
00:27:21,800 --> 00:27:25,100
luxurious clothes and rare treasures from all over the world.

408
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:28,200
I have to plead with the shopkeeper...

409
00:27:28,200 --> 00:27:31,400
to sell me the tea and the tea set.

410
00:27:32,400 --> 00:27:35,200
Wuyou, I know that you love tea.

411
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:38,200
If only we could go for tea tasting in the Moon Embrace Teahouse...

412
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:40,700
and take a look at their Rare Item Chest...

413
00:27:40,700 --> 00:27:42,200
Moon Embrace Teahouse, right?

414
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:45,200
That's right. Come along with me.

415
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:48,400
This is indeed a good tea.

416
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:52,300
But I think it doesn't taste very pure.

417
00:27:52,300 --> 00:27:55,400
It's not pure? Impossible.

418
00:27:55,400 --> 00:27:57,500
I can't possibly lie to you, Wuyou.

419
00:27:57,500 --> 00:27:59,000
Do you think you can lie to me?

420
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:01,300
- No.
- Fine.

421
00:28:01,300 --> 00:28:02,900
On behalf of this tea,

422
00:28:02,900 --> 00:28:05,200
I'll go with you this time.

423
00:28:07,100 --> 00:28:09,400
[Moon Embrace Teahouse]

424
00:28:16,800 --> 00:28:20,000
How rude. How can you just go away
after running into me?

425
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,600
Mistress, you are here.

426
00:28:48,600 --> 00:28:51,000
We have been waiting for you.

427
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:55,600
Although it's far, I have arrived safely.

428
00:28:55,600 --> 00:28:58,000
This teahouse is brimming with customers.

429
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,600
Looks like it's doing well.

430
00:28:59,600 --> 00:29:01,100
Good soil to plant the tea tree in.

431
00:29:01,100 --> 00:29:03,400
And the best water to steep the tea leaves in.

432
00:29:03,400 --> 00:29:04,600
Our master has high aspirations.

433
00:29:04,600 --> 00:29:07,200
Of course, we'll have good business.

434
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:09,400
You might be doing well.

435
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:13,300
But I heard that you are already carried away with your success.

436
00:29:13,300 --> 00:29:16,500
Just like the kite that flies high above.

437
00:29:16,500 --> 00:29:18,300
We are no longer of importance to you.

438
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:20,400
That is not true, Mistress.

439
00:29:20,400 --> 00:29:25,000
No matter how high the kite flies, the master still holds the string.

440
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:27,000
Since you are already here personally,

441
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:29,000
from now on, you'll be the decision-maker...

442
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:31,300
for every matter regarding this teahouse.

443
00:29:31,300 --> 00:29:34,300
Looks like you are the shopkeeper of Moon Embrace Teahouse.

444
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:38,000
Yes, I am. Greetings, Mistress.

445
00:29:45,800 --> 00:29:47,800
This way please, Mistress.

446
00:30:27,600 --> 00:30:29,000
Greetings, Princess.

447
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:30,900
Be at ease.

448
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:34,400
From now on, when I'm here, I won't be a princess.

449
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:36,900
You just need to address me as mistress.

450
00:30:36,900 --> 00:30:38,900
Yes, Mistress.

451
00:30:38,900 --> 00:30:43,300
Before this, there were rumors about the princess of Western Qi being ugly.

452
00:30:43,300 --> 00:30:45,600
Is that the work of Moon Embrace Teahouse and the kite?

453
00:30:45,600 --> 00:30:48,000
You are indeed brilliant.

454
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:50,400
His Majesty knows that you didn't do it willingly.

455
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:53,400
So, he wants to buy you as much time as he can.

456
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:55,600
I understand the troubles he took.

457
00:30:55,600 --> 00:30:58,800
We'll come back to this matter after half a year.

458
00:30:58,800 --> 00:31:02,000
I think you know the purpose of me coming here.

459
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:05,400
We are still searching for "The Book of Mountains and Rivers."

460
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:09,200
Can you tell me more about "The Book of Mountains and Rivers?"

461
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:10,800
Have a seat.

462
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:19,000
Sixteen years ago,

463
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:21,500
there were a few major incidents in Northern Lin.

464
00:31:21,500 --> 00:31:23,400
For example, Fu Yuan passed away in a fire.

465
00:31:23,400 --> 00:31:24,800
Fu Yuan?

466
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:27,000
Fu Yuan is the youngest daughter of the previous Emperor of Chen.

467
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:29,600
Before Northern Lin reclaims their lands, they aligned with Chen.

468
00:31:29,600 --> 00:31:31,600
Fu Yuan was set for marriage.

469
00:31:31,600 --> 00:31:33,600
In the end, Fu Yuan had to leave her home town...

470
00:31:33,600 --> 00:31:35,300
to marry the Emperor of Northern Lin.

471
00:31:35,300 --> 00:31:38,100
After the emperor reclaimed his lands, he appointed her as empress.

472
00:31:38,100 --> 00:31:41,800
But after that, they turned against each other for reasons we don't know.

473
00:31:41,800 --> 00:31:43,600
Fu Yuan was sent to the Cold Harem.

474
00:31:43,600 --> 00:31:46,000
And she passed away in an accidental fire.

475
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:49,000
So, this fire is related to "The Book of Mountains and Rivers."

476
00:31:49,000 --> 00:31:51,600
We are yet to be sure about the relations.

477
00:31:51,600 --> 00:31:55,500
But there are a few other incidents that happened in the same year.

478
00:31:55,500 --> 00:31:59,000
Emperor of Northern Lin's most favorite concubine passed away, too.

479
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:01,200
These two women were eyesores for each other.

480
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:03,800
But they died one after another in accidents.

481
00:32:03,800 --> 00:32:08,400
Not long after, the ex-chief minister, Qin Yong, and his family were killed.

482
00:32:08,400 --> 00:32:11,000
Word is, he was related to Lady Yun's death.

483
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:13,600
From then on, the Emperor of Northern Lin has imposed a ban.

484
00:32:13,600 --> 00:32:17,400
Everything regarding Qin Yong, including the book, became taboo.

485
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:19,200
Nobody has dared to mention it after that.

486
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:21,200
There is no word about it at all?

487
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:24,400
Although Qin Yong is dead, many of his former subordinates are still alive.

488
00:32:24,400 --> 00:32:26,200
I started my investigation from here.

489
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:28,200
And I did find a person.

490
00:32:29,090 --> 00:32:31,710
[An Elegant Home Is Abundantly Peaceful]

491
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:35,000
Princess.

492
00:32:37,390 --> 00:32:38,789
The night feast is ready.

493
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:41,400
Please inform the princess, Miss Lian Xin.

494
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:44,100
When are we going to start the feast?

495
00:32:44,100 --> 00:32:46,000
The princess hasn't been sleeping well lately.

496
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:47,500
She is still napping.

497
00:32:47,500 --> 00:32:50,600
When she wakes, I'll inform her.

498
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:53,400
I'll take my leave then.

499
00:32:58,900 --> 00:33:02,000
- Ling Yue.
- She's gone?

500
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:04,000
Why is the princess still not here?

501
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:05,440
I'll go and bring the princess back.

502
00:33:05,440 --> 00:33:07,400
Both of you stay here.

503
00:33:13,600 --> 00:33:15,900
Wuyou, we are here.

504
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:20,400
If you want to drink tea in Zhongshan,

505
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:22,800
everybody will come to Moon Embrace Teahouse.

506
00:33:22,800 --> 00:33:24,600
But if they want to listen to music and drink wine,

507
00:33:24,600 --> 00:33:26,900
they will go to House of Fragrance.

508
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:28,800
The Flower Queen of the House of Fragrance, Miss Chen Yu...

509
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:32,400
is indeed a beauty that put the moon and flowers to shame.

510
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:35,600
But nobody knows her true identity.

511
00:33:35,600 --> 00:33:39,200
So, Miss Chen Yu has news about "The Book of Mountains and Rivers."

512
00:33:39,200 --> 00:33:41,000
I'm still not sure if she has...

513
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:43,200
any usable information.

514
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:44,600
But I'm sure that...

515
00:33:44,600 --> 00:33:48,200
her father who was punished is the former subordinate of Qin Yong.

516
00:33:49,600 --> 00:33:51,300
Good.

517
00:33:52,600 --> 00:33:54,200
She is an important lead.

518
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:56,200
You have to investigate more about her.

519
00:33:56,200 --> 00:34:01,000
By the way, is there anyone looking out for her?

520
