556
00:38:12,700 --> 00:38:16,000
so that one day, he'd have the chance to clean up the officialdom...

557
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:19,600
and give a glimmer of hope to those with real talents.

558
00:38:19,600 --> 00:38:21,000
Wuyou, I just wanted to help him.

559
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:23,400
I don't know that it'd be like this.

560
00:38:24,600 --> 00:38:27,400
So what if he's a good officer?

561
